content: I don't have access to the specific requirements or prerequisites for the startup garage program. however, based on my research, you must be a current stanford university student to participate in the program. additionally, admission to the program is competitive, and they look for students with a demonstrated interest and commitment to entrepreneurship, a strong team with diverse skills, and a well-articulated business concept. it is likely that you will need to go through an application process, which may include submitting a business plan, a pitch presentation, and possibly an interview. i would recommend visiting the program's website or contacting the program directly for more specific information on the requirements and application process.
